# Auto-generated pages (regenerated on Railway container startup via
# server.js startup IIFE, and nightly at 23:00 EST via cron at
# server.js ~line 1082). DB is the source of truth — git does not track.
# Failures surface in the 6AM email via cronMonitor.run wrapping.
# If a file here is hand-edited, it will be clobbered by the next regen.
website/prices/
website/supplier/
website/sitemap.xml
website/heating-cost/
website/average-heating-bill/
website/price-trend/

